OL,5, Actress and Strictly Come Dancing      
OL,6, champion Rose Ayling-Ellis is to become
OL,7, the first celebrity to sign a CBeebies 
OL,8, bedtime story this Sunday.             
OL,10,FAyling-Ellis, 27, who has been deaf    
OL,11,Fsince birth, will tell the tale Can    
OL,12,FBears Ski? in British Sign Language    
OL,13,F(BSL), to mark Deaf Awareness Week.    
OL,15,FThe story of a young bear draws on the 
OL,16,Fauthor's own experience to show how it 
OL,17,Ffeels to be deaf in a hearing world.   
OL,19,FAyling-Ellis said she hoped it would   
OL,20,Finspire children to learn to sign.     
